@subsubsection boundaryLatticePoints
@cindex boundaryLatticePoints
@table @code
@item @strong{Syntax:}
@code{Polymake::boundaryLatticePoints(} polytope p @code{)}
@item @strong{Assume:}
p bounded
@item @strong{Type:}
intmat
@item @strong{Purpose:}
intmat, whose rows are the lattice points on the relative boundary of p.
@item @strong{Example:}
